flowchart TD
    subgraph Client ["Client Layer"]
        A[Browser Request: dev.buildwithruud.com/admin]
    end

    subgraph Ingress ["Routing & Ingress Layer"]
        B[Caddy Proxy / K8s Ingress] -->|Preserves Host Header| C[Leptos SSR / CSR Application Router]
    end

    subgraph Axum ["Axum Middleware & Router Tier"]
        C -->|HTTP Request| D[Axum AppInstance Middleware]
