        F -->|Inject resolved Tenant ID & App Context| G[Axum Request Extensions]
    end

    subgraph Service ["Service & Data Access Tier"]
        G -->|Matches Route| H[Server Function / Handler]
        H -->|Extract Tenant ID from Context| I[SeaORM Query Builder]
        I -->|Inject Column::TenantId.eq| J[Execute Scope-Filtered Query]
    end

    subgraph DB ["PostgreSQL Database"]
        J -->|SELECT * FROM resume_entries WHERE tenant_id = resolved_id| K[(Filtered Results)]
    end

    A --> B
    K -->|Return isolated data only| Client
